<main id="content" class="content"> <header> <h1 class="title">Prayer for Trinity Sunday</h1>
 <p class="subtitle" role="doc-subtitle">Jun 16, 2019</p>
</header> <p>
Triune God,
</p>

 <p>
In those times <br></br>
that we feel alone, <br></br>
lost in the crowd, <br></br>
and disconnected <br></br>
from those around us, <br></br>
we take comfort in knowing <br></br>
that at the center of reality <br></br>
is an unending community of love, <br></br>
and that we, your children, <br></br>
have been invited into <br></br>
the eternal fellowship <br></br>
that is the <br></br>
Father, <br></br>
Son, <br></br>
and Holy Spirit, <br></br>
three persons, <br></br>
but one God, <br></br>
forever and ever.
</p>

 <p>
 <i>Amen</i>
</p>
</main>